EventType definitions\\n- `/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/types.go` - HookType, HookInput structs\\n\\n**Session phase machine:**\\n- `/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli/cmd/entire/cli/session/phase.go` - Transition logic\\n\\n**Strategy hooks:**\\n- `/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli/cmd/entire/cli/strategy/hooks.go` - Git hook installation\\n- `/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli/cmd/entire/cli/strategy/hook_managers.go` - External hook manager detection\\n\\n**Agent implementations:**\\n- Claude Code: `/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/claudecode/lifecycle.go` + hooks.go\\n- Gemini CLI: `/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/geminicli/lifecycle.go` + hooks.go\\n- OpenCode: `/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/opencode/lifecycle.go` + hooks.go\\n- Cursor: `/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/cursor/lifecycle.go` + hooks.go\\n- Factory AI Droid: `/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/factoryaidroid/lifecycle.go` + hooks.go\\n\\n---\\n\\nThis architecture achieves several design goals:\\n\\n1. **Normalization:** Native agent hooks translate to canonical EventType/HookType\\n2. **Extensibility:** New agents implement HookSupport.ParseHookEvent to add their hooks\\n3. **Statelessness:** Hooks are pure functions (no side effects in parse phase)\\n4. **Idempotency:** Hook installation checks existing config before modifying\\n5. **Backward compatibility:** Unknown hook types/fields preserved via raw JSON marshaling\\n6. **Tool-aware:** Claude Code supports tool-use matchers for context-specific hooks\\n7. **Phase-driven:** Session lifecycle managed by explicit state machine, not implicit hook counters\"}],\"totalDurationMs\":71359,\"totalTokens\":123894,\"totalToolUseCount\":31,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":2896,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":117250,\"output_tokens\":3748,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"